{"tid":1391873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會唔會剪條文宣影片鼓勵人8月5罷工？","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:45:36.000Z","uid":119291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f299465bb102373e9df1bf7b2df5ce93800bebfb","tid":1391873,"uid":119291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:36:10.000Z","msg":"想話文宣圖好多 如果剪條文宣片鼓勵大家罷工<br />\n你地覺得點睇？主要以煽情激勵為主<br />\n目標對象係和理非/淺黃 希望做到係fb同whatsapp瘋傳效果<br />\n<br />\n感覺自從721之後大家都聚焦係黑社會同警察<br />\n同偏向憤怒居多 <br />\n建議呢條片可以有2個大方向<br />\n<br />\n1. 總結返由69至宜家既大事, 可以有少部分示威者被警察蝦/黑社會蝦既片段 但唔好太多,可以剪多d比較正面既 例如一D香港人團結畫面<br />\n<br />\n2.聚焦返係5大訴求同普選<br />\n<br />\n呢條片雖然係雨革既片 但每次睇都覺得好激勵人心 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8celowZ-QF8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8celowZ-QF8&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFkn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=c1c35aa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8celowZ-QF8</a><br />\n係一條可以用黎做參考既片<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得點～我剪片唔叻 但可以幫忙搵source<br />\n剪片叻/ 有興趣巴絲可以加我tg一齊傾下<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/szzecc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fszzecc&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFkn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=1709365e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/szzecc</a>"},{"pid":"ac76067b0adae09372d60186a1604e8852b65cf4","tid":1391873,"uid":295484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"[極多圖] 一齊號召公務員出黎集會罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「救人！」世紀最大救義士唯一方法 正式上線 第一波<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391669</a>"},{"pid":"d42762ed9811b83d447c78b2447b821689d837cc","tid":1391873,"uid":119291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":